data.description: This stunning lake front property featuring a dock leading directly to the water. NO FLOOD ZONE, NEW ROOF, HVAC has been maintained every year by American Home Shield and can be transferred to the new owner. This home has been meticulously taken care of and it shows in every aspect. The kitchen is a chefs dream, really great cabinet organizers and features only 3 year old Samsung grey stainless steel appliances, and tons of cabinet space. 2 living areas make entertaining a breeze. Cedar wall in primary closet for added luxury. High cathedral ceilings. Fully fenced in yard with curb it flower beds. Shed is already hooked up with electric. Ring cameras convey. Only $10 a month for the HOA and it includes trash pick up and all the amenities the Silver Springs Shores Community Center; pool access, fitness center and more.  Call today to see this beautiful home!    Seller has a full inspection report on this home for peace of mind of future buyers.
